Robbie was published in 12 numbers in 1976 and 1977, with features Robbie, Wippy & Trotty. Minou-Cat had 32 issues, 1975 to 1977, and features Minou-Cat, Miss Tigry, Mistik et Gigott, & Trompinet. The features are described, with dates and issue numbers, and minor features in Minou-Cat are listed. All three magazines were small format color publications for young children.
